<Paragraph>Essential Presentation library has support for inserting images in a PowerPoint presentation.</Paragraph>
<Paragraph>This sample demonstrates how to insert an image in a PowerPoint slide.</Paragraph>
<BlockUIContainer>
<TextBlock Style="{DynamicResource HeaderTextStyle}"><Bold>Features:</Bold></TextBlock>
</BlockUIContainer>
<Paragraph>
This sample demonstrates the following features:
</Paragraph>
<List>
<ListItem><Paragraph>Add new images to a PowerPoint slide.</Paragraph></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph>Insert, delete, replace, and format pictures in a PowerPoint slide.</Paragraph></ListItem>
</List>

<Paragraph><Bold>Note:</Bold> This library supports creation, manipulation and conversion to PDF/image for .pptx format alone.</Paragraph>

